                    "latex": [],
                    "tables": []
                }
            ],
            "correctAnswer": [
                "A",
                "B",
                "C"
            ],
            "solution": {
                "text": "• \nEquivalence problem for Turing machine is \nUndecidable. \n• \nRegularity problem for Turing machine is \nUndecidable. \n• \nTotality (Completeness) problem for Turing \nmachine is Undecidable. \n• \nGiven a Turing machine M, decide if M takes \nmore than 1073 steps on every string is \nDecidable.",
                "images": [],
                "latex": [],
                "tables": []
            }
